#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.gcompris.appdata.xml:34
msgid ""
"Currently GCompris offers in excess of 100 activities and more are being "
"developed. GCompris is free software, that means that you can adapt it to "
"your own needs, improve it and, most importantly, share it with children "
"everywhere."
msgstr ""
"Jelenleg a GCompris több mint 100 féle tevékenységet kínál és több is "
"fejlesztés alatt áll. A Gcompris ingyenes szoftver, amely azt jelenti, "
"kedvedre átalakíthatod, fejlesztheted, és a legfontosabb: megoszthatod "
"bármely gyerekkel."

